4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for those with no prior knowledge aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks, consisting of three live online classes each week, with a maximum class size of 16 students. Participants gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, networking, and server administration, while mastering cloud security, penetration testing, and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, students receive an official 4Geeks Certificate, recognized by multiple institutions. The courses are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop